# This is a single-file game: all artwork ships embedded as data URIs inside
# index.html, so the repo never needs loose image files. Ignore every image so
# debug screenshots, source art, and reference shots can't get pushed by accident.
# (If you ever genuinely need to commit one, use: git add -f <file>)
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp
*.bmp

# reference screenshots from the original game (not ours to publish) — kept
# explicit for documentation; already covered by the rules above
example.png
p1demo.png
bug1.png
bug-again.png
